| github_url | TEXT | |
| last_update | TEXT | Most recent textual update |
| created_at | TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW() | |
| updated_at | TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW() | Trigger auto-bumps on UPDATE |
| resolved_at | TIMESTAMPTZ | |

